    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Large wooden puck-like objects used in the Dutch game of platte bol and for other traditional Dutch games. For similar objects used for ice hockey, use "hockey pucks."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
